            "title": "九台農商獲吉林金控溢價逾70%提私有化",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">九台農商銀行(06122)及吉林金控聯合公布，吉林金控提出私有化九台農商建議，每股H股私有化價格0.7元，較停牌前收市價0.44元溢價70.73%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公布稱，要約人將不會提高要約價。當私有化完成，公司將申請退市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">此外，吉林金控將就收購所有已發行內資股作出全面現金要約，，內資股要約價現金人民幣0.63元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">私有化涉及總現金代價H股6.77億港元，內資股25.88億元人民幣。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">H股要約須經出席的獨立H股股東表決權中至少75%投票表決批准方生效。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一方面︳九台農商銀行發盈警，預告截靅024年12月31日年度虧損1.7億元至1.9億元人民幣之問，股份續停牌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15062670-%e4%b9%9d%e5%8f%b0%e8%be%b2%e5%95%86%e7%8d%b2%e5%90%89%e6%9e%97%e9%87%91%e6%8e%a7%e6%ba%a2%e5%83%b9%e9%80%be70%e6%8f%90%e7%a7%81%e6%9c%89%e5%8c%96",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250704-_JILIN_JIUTAI_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-04 09:25:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股開市︱失守二萬四 恒指跌169點報23900點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股隔晚半日市造好，未能支撐港股回升。恒生指數再度失守二萬四，今早開市報23900點，跌169點或0.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5194點，跌39點或0.75%；國企指數以8585點開市，跌62點或0.73%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)落實發行120.23億元可交換阿里健康(00241)股份的債券；阿里巴巴今早於競價時段以105.2元開市，跌0.94%；阿里健康則開報4.3元，跌4.87%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135119_source-web_00241阿里健康-1_source-web_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135119_source-web_00241阿里健康-1_source-web_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里健康官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">樂普生物(02157)折讓約10.99%配股；該股今早開報5.62元，跌0.36%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多點數智(02586)官宣正籌備申請穩定幣牌照，該股今早開報12.8元，逆市飆14.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安井食品(02648)今早登場，以60元開市，與招股價相同。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15062709-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e5%9b%9b-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c169%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123900%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-04 09:25:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
