            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報23933點，跌119點，較上日現貨收市價24069點低水137點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5206點，跌17點，低水28點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報8592點，跌45點，低水56點。</p>\n</div>",
